        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44183568/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44183568/" class="">第114页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lns/" class=" " title="寕">寕</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44183568">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">并不是这些人比其它的律师更聪明，只是因为他们工作了几十年之后所磨练出的技巧，突然之间变得很有价值。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-22 13:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>并不是这些人比其它的律师更聪明，只是因为他们工作了几十年之后所磨练出的技巧，突然之间变得很有价值。</p>
